  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.42,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.42,
      "end": 36.34,
      "text": "8월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.34,
      "end": 39.4,
      "text": "고독한 드라큘라와 몬스터로 변해버린"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.4,
      "end": 43.14,
      "text": "위시본 가족의 한바탕 소동을 다룬 애니메이션"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.14,
      "end": 44.54,
      "text": "몬스터 패밀리"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.54,
      "end": 54.4,
      "text": "새로운 한 주이기도 하고 행복한 월요일기를 하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.4,
      "end": 55.14,
      "text": "그리고 또"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.14,
      "end": 69.2,
      "text": "오늘이 이 영화를 다루는 마지막 시간인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.2,
      "end": 74.1,
      "text": "과연 우리 위시본 가족이 원래 모습으로 돌아올 수 있을지"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.1,
      "end": 75.28,
      "text": "너무 기대가 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.78,
      "end": 80.34,
      "text": "Yeah, I hope they go back to their original human being selves."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.68,
      "end": 82.52,
      "text": "But it's up to them, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.74,
      "end": 83.02,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.3,
      "end": 87.76,
      "text": "The spell can only be broken if they are happy, truly happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.06,
      "end": 90.44,
      "text": "And happiness is not objective."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.8,
      "end": 93.14,
      "text": "There's no one definition of happiness."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.66,
      "end": 94.68,
      "text": "It's very subjective."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.06,
      "end": 96.52,
      "text": "So it's up to the family."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.86,
      "end": 97.74,
      "text": "Are you happy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.1,
      "end": 99.68,
      "text": "저한테 지금 질문하시는 거예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.68,
      "end": 101.62,
      "text": "I'm talking to the wishbone family."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.84,
      "end": 102.8,
      "text": "근데 대답하셔도"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.8,
      "end": 104.52,
      "text": "Sure, I'm happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.4,
      "end": 110.44,
      "text": "네, 위시본 가족도 스스로들이 참 행복하다라고 느꼈으면 좋겠어요, 그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.96,
      "end": 113.88,
      "text": "말씀하신 대로 it is up to them, themselves, 그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.14,
      "end": 114.4,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.58,
      "end": 115.48,
      "text": "But are you happy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.88,
      "end": 116.76,
      "text": "Yeah, sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.94,
      "end": 117.42,
      "text": "How about you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.62,
      "end": 120.42,
      "text": "And what do you think about the happiness of your family?"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.54,
      "end": 121.22,
      "text": "Of my family?"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.32,
      "end": 121.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.5,
      "end": 125.9,
      "text": "When you have a family, happiness is impossible."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.74,
      "end": 127.22,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.4,
      "end": 128.14,
      "text": "Totally impossible."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.14,
      "end": 130.06,
      "text": "Why do you say it like that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.74,
      "end": 134.04,
      "text": "I'm half kidding, but it's very subjective."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.38,
      "end": 134.72,
      "text": "Oh, right."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.74,
      "end": 139.2,
      "text": "And there's no such thing as, every day is happy, and I feel great."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.02,
      "end": 144.0,
      "text": "As this movie taught us, you take the ups and you take the downs."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.4,
      "end": 148.3,
      "text": "You take the arguments, and you take the wonderful conversations."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.72,
      "end": 150.04,
      "text": "You have to take everything."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.4,
      "end": 152.58,
      "text": "You gave me very realistic answers."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.26,
      "end": 153.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.18,
      "end": 156.86,
      "text": "Do you have a different definition?"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.86,
      "end": 183.04,
      "text": "Oh, sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.04,
      "end": 183.96,
      "text": "Me, too."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.52,
      "end": 187.52,
      "text": "I think many of us are like that, and that's not a bad thing."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.58,
      "end": 187.86,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.04,
      "end": 198.18,
      "text": "But for family, you have to show your real self, your good and your bad, and you have to accept each other for who each one of you, each one of us are."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.18,
      "end": 201.2,
      "text": "우리 청취자 여러분들도 많이 공감을 하실 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.98,
      "end": 204.08,
      "text": "일단 오늘 장면 들어보고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.18,
      "end": 206.19,
      "text": "You were right, Faith."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.81,
      "end": 208.73,
      "text": "I'm really good at messing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.87,
      "end": 209.55,
      "text": "No, mom."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.97,
      "end": 211.01,
      "text": "You were right."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.73,
      "end": 212.25,
      "text": "I was."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.3,
      "end": 216.1,
      "text": "It doesn't matter if people look at me and see an ugly mummy."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.66,
      "end": 219.17,
      "text": "I know who I am under all these bandages."
    },
    {
      "start": 219.17,
      "end": 222.25,
      "text": "And it's not that much fun being scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.65,
      "end": 223.93,
      "text": "It's actually kind of lonely."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.65,
      "end": 227.51,
      "text": "I'm sorry I said all those awful things."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.27,
      "end": 230.05,
      "text": "I wouldn't want any other family."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.05,
      "end": 239.3,
      "text": "드라큘라에게 지금 붙잡힌 상황이긴 한데, fortunately, however, they realized family values."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.3,
      "end": 240.06,
      "text": "They do."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.62,
      "end": 243.24,
      "text": "They were happy, after all."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.36,
      "end": 243.84,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.16,
      "end": 244.98,
      "text": "Good for them."
    },
    {
      "start": 245.34,
      "end": 245.46,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 245.54,
      "end": 246.38,
      "text": "They broke the spell."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.84,
      "end": 249.52,
      "text": "At first, they could not break it."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.66,
      "end": 251.76,
      "text": "They tried to attack 드라큘라."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.88,
      "end": 252.12,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.12,
      "end": 261.22,
      "text": "Remember, he was taking a bath, 목욕하고 계셨고, the Lazarus bath, to make his skin more young and supple."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.22,
      "end": 268.12,
      "text": "But they tried to pour holy water in the bath to kill 드라큘라 or to hurt him."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.36,
      "end": 269.4,
      "text": "It didn't work out."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.94,
      "end": 271.3,
      "text": "So, 드라큘라 came out."
    },
    {
      "start": 271.46,
      "end": 272.38,
      "text": "He attacked them."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.8,
      "end": 273.42,
      "text": "They fought."
    },
    {
      "start": 274.0,
      "end": 277.9,
      "text": "And the family ended up coming out on top."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.1,
      "end": 278.54,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.96,
      "end": 279.7,
      "text": "정말 다행입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.7,
      "end": 282.72,
      "text": "지금 굉장히 briefly하게 summarize를 해주셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 283.32,
      "end": 285.52,
      "text": "일단 단어들을 한번 점검을 해볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.12,
      "end": 287.04,
      "text": "Messing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 287.24,
      "end": 290.12,
      "text": "Messing up이라는 구조가 들리는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.74,
      "end": 291.32,
      "text": "Mess up."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.68,
      "end": 293.74,
      "text": "Mess up이라는 것도 많이 들어보셨을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.88,
      "end": 294.0,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.32,
      "end": 297.52,
      "text": "엉망으로 만들다, 다 망치다 라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.8,
      "end": 298.46,
      "text": "Messing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.48,
      "end": 299.3,
      "text": "Messing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.6,
      "end": 300.98,
      "text": "I keep messing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.42,
      "end": 303.04,
      "text": "이거 많이 하는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.04,
      "end": 304.1,
      "text": "계속 망치고 있어."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.56,
      "end": 305.26,
      "text": "그런 날 있죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.64,
      "end": 306.8,
      "text": "When you blame yourself."
    },
    {
      "start": 308.04,
      "end": 309.12,
      "text": "Being scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.12,
      "end": 312.1,
      "text": "Being scary 라는 조합이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.34,
      "end": 318.7,
      "text": "그래서 뭔가 좀 두려워하게 하는 혹은 두렵게 하는 이 정도로 해석할 수 있을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.84,
      "end": 319.88,
      "text": "Do you like being scary?"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.14,
      "end": 322.88,
      "text": "I like being scary to my little girls sometimes."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.04,
      "end": 323.42,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.52,
      "end": 327.02,
      "text": "I like scaring them because it's so fun to see their reaction."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.46,
      "end": 327.88,
      "text": "It's weird."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.96,
      "end": 330.14,
      "text": "I get pleasure out of their reaction."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.14,
      "end": 331.76,
      "text": "Oh, stop it."
    },
    {
      "start": 331.76,
      "end": 332.52,
      "text": "뭔 죄예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 333.84,
      "end": 334.38,
      "text": "가끔."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.48,
      "end": 334.64,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.9,
      "end": 336.0,
      "text": "그래서 하니까 하지 말라고."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.22,
      "end": 337.4,
      "text": "괴물 그만하라고."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.54,
      "end": 340.64,
      "text": "근데 제가 아연할 때 막 괴물 해줘."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.74,
      "end": 341.34,
      "text": "괴물 해줘."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.34,
      "end": 343.04,
      "text": "굉장히 중독적인가 봅니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.4,
      "end": 344.96,
      "text": "연기력이 아주 훌륭하신가 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.1,
      "end": 346.82,
      "text": "I don't think so, but it's scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.04,
      "end": 349.14,
      "text": "Awful things."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.48,
      "end": 350.16,
      "text": "Awful."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.36,
      "end": 351.46,
      "text": "이거 많이 들어보셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.6,
      "end": 353.26,
      "text": "끔찍한 이라는 형용사잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.82,
      "end": 356.38,
      "text": "Awful things라고 해서 끔찍한 것들."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.62,
      "end": 358.02,
      "text": "이렇게 보시면 되겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 358.6,
      "end": 360.14,
      "text": "이 내용 한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 377.01,
      "end": 378.59,
      "text": "It's not that much fun being scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.99,
      "end": 380.29,
      "text": "It's actually a kind of lonely."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.05,
      "end": 383.87,
      "text": "I'm sorry I said all those awful things."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.13,
      "end": 386.41,
      "text": "I wouldn't want any other family."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.99,
      "end": 389.15,
      "text": "Oh, precious families."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.07,
      "end": 390.31,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.53,
      "end": 392.51,
      "text": "This is the big makeup scene."
    },
    {
      "start": 392.63,
      "end": 393.03,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 393.31,
      "end": 393.87,
      "text": "They fought."
    },
    {
      "start": 394.13,
      "end": 395.77,
      "text": "They went their separate ways."
    },
    {
      "start": 395.85,
      "end": 397.65,
      "text": "And now they all made up."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.91,
      "end": 398.87,
      "text": "They're happy again."
    },
    {
      "start": 399.01,
      "end": 400.53,
      "text": "And they're human beings."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.73,
      "end": 401.23,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 401.45,
      "end": 403.33,
      "text": "이 전체적인 영화 줄거리 중에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.33,
      "end": 407.09,
      "text": "이 부분이 가장 감동적인 부분이었던 걸로 기억을 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 407.33,
      "end": 408.23,
      "text": "It was a little touching."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.35,
      "end": 409.45,
      "text": "A little cheesy."
    },
    {
      "start": 409.71,
      "end": 410.91,
      "text": "But touching too."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.03,
      "end": 414.17,
      "text": "자, 어떤 내용인지 자세히 살펴볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.57,
      "end": 416.47,
      "text": "You were right, Faye."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.35,
      "end": 420.25,
      "text": "엄마가 이제 딸한테 이야기하는 장면입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 420.35,
      "end": 421.59,
      "text": "You were right, Faye."
    },
    {
      "start": 422.01,
      "end": 423.53,
      "text": "Faye야, 네 말이 맞아."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.39,
      "end": 426.75,
      "text": "I'm really good at messing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 427.15,
      "end": 430.03,
      "text": "여기서 be good at 이라는 구조를 썼어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 430.25,
      "end": 432.03,
      "text": "난 무엇뭇에 능숙하다, 잘한다."
    },
    {
      "start": 432.15,
      "end": 433.15,
      "text": "I'm good at English."
    },
    {
      "start": 433.15,
      "end": 434.37,
      "text": "Oh, 난 영어를 잘해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 434.39,
      "end": 435.11,
      "text": "I'm good at swimming."
    },
    {
      "start": 435.31,
      "end": 436.25,
      "text": "난 수영을 잘해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.31,
      "end": 437.19,
      "text": "보통 좋은 거잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 437.27,
      "end": 437.59,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 437.91,
      "end": 440.07,
      "text": "근데 여기서는요, 굉장히 아이러니컬하게"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.07,
      "end": 443.01,
      "text": "I'm really good at messing up 이라고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 443.75,
      "end": 447.01,
      "text": "엉망으로 만드는 것에 아주 능숙하지."
    },
    {
      "start": 447.21,
      "end": 447.69,
      "text": "라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 447.79,
      "end": 449.23,
      "text": "She's been critical of herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 449.23,
      "end": 453.31,
      "text": "No, mom, you were right."
    },
    {
      "start": 453.55,
      "end": 454.93,
      "text": "그랬더니 반전입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 455.19,
      "end": 459.47,
      "text": "Whoa, this is the daughter that does not get along with her mom."
    },
    {
      "start": 459.83,
      "end": 461.81,
      "text": "She's in her teenage years."
    },
    {
      "start": 461.81,
      "end": 463.01,
      "text": "Very sensitive."
    },
    {
      "start": 463.01,
      "end": 463.49,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.19,
      "end": 465.01,
      "text": "큰 반전이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.11,
      "end": 465.29,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.47,
      "end": 467.35,
      "text": "예상하지 못한 대답을 들으셨는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.57,
      "end": 469.83,
      "text": "No, mom, you were right."
    },
    {
      "start": 470.27,
      "end": 471.05,
      "text": "아니에요, 엄마."
    },
    {
      "start": 471.39,
      "end": 472.55,
      "text": "엄마가 옳았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.81,
      "end": 473.89,
      "text": "엄마 말이 맞았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.09,
      "end": 474.49,
      "text": "라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.49,
      "end": 476.35,
      "text": "And mom is shocked."
    },
    {
      "start": 476.59,
      "end": 477.25,
      "text": "너무 놀랐죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.37,
      "end": 478.47,
      "text": "I was?"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.87,
      "end": 479.57,
      "text": "I was?"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.85,
      "end": 480.29,
      "text": "이랬어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 480.39,
      "end": 481.07,
      "text": "너무 놀래가지고."
    },
    {
      "start": 481.65,
      "end": 481.89,
      "text": "내가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.33,
      "end": 483.11,
      "text": "내가 옳았어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 483.37,
      "end": 483.95,
      "text": "라는 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.09,
      "end": 484.71,
      "text": "You were right."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.79,
      "end": 485.57,
      "text": "No, you were right."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.61,
      "end": 486.41,
      "text": "No, you were right."
    },
    {
      "start": 486.41,
      "end": 487.35,
      "text": "Isn't this sweet?"
    },
    {
      "start": 487.65,
      "end": 487.85,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.95,
      "end": 488.87,
      "text": "The family's happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 488.97,
      "end": 489.63,
      "text": "Sounds so sweet."
    },
    {
      "start": 490.81,
      "end": 495.19,
      "text": "It doesn't matter if people look at me and see an ugly mummy."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.63,
      "end": 503.43,
      "text": "자, 이 문장은요, 특히 if라는 게 접속사 weather하고 똑같은 의미로 해석을 하셔야 되는 용법이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 503.43,
      "end": 508.97,
      "text": "일단은 it doesn't matter 이라고 시작을 했으니까 중요하지 않아요 라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 509.37,
      "end": 520.73,
      "text": "If people look at me, 사람들이 날 보는 것이, and see an ugly mummy 라고 했으니까 그리고 날 못생긴 미라로 보든지 아니든지 이거는 제가 순차적으로 해석을 해드린 거고"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.73,
      "end": 526.67,
      "text": "좀 더 자연스럽게 의역을 한다면 사람들이 저를 흉측한 미라로 봐도 저는 상관없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 526.67,
      "end": 528.57,
      "text": "이게 자연스럽습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 528.65,
      "end": 529.63,
      "text": "콤플렉스 있었는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 529.63,
      "end": 536.55,
      "text": "She was so worried about looking pretty for the boys, and now it doesn't matter."
    },
    {
      "start": 538.05,
      "end": 541.49,
      "text": "I know who I am under all these bandages."
    },
    {
      "start": 541.85,
      "end": 542.65,
      "text": "멋지네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 542.87,
      "end": 544.43,
      "text": "멋진 대답의 연속입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 544.79,
      "end": 549.01,
      "text": "I know who I am under all these bandages."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.01,
      "end": 552.05,
      "text": "저는 알아요, 제가 누군지."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.61,
      "end": 559.27,
      "text": "그리고 under all these bandages 라고 했으니까 이 붕대들 아래에 있는 제가 누군지 알아요라는 거거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 560.23,
      "end": 561.73,
      "text": "저는 내면의 저를 알아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.95,
      "end": 562.59,
      "text": "이거 괜찮네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 562.83,
      "end": 567.75,
      "text": "아, she didn't know herself even before she had all those bandages."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.91,
      "end": 568.23,
      "text": "Definitely."
    },
    {
      "start": 568.23,
      "end": 570.33,
      "text": "But now she found her herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 570.49,
      "end": 571.33,
      "text": "She's confident."
    },
    {
      "start": 571.49,
      "end": 571.75,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 571.87,
      "end": 573.21,
      "text": "She restored her confidence."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.37,
      "end": 577.39,
      "text": "그리고 여기에서 붕대라는 단어로 bandages라는 단어가 들렸습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 577.43,
      "end": 578.05,
      "text": "bandages."
    },
    {
      "start": 578.55,
      "end": 581.29,
      "text": "흔히 말하는, 미국 사람이 말하는 bandaid."
    },
    {
      "start": 581.39,
      "end": 583.85,
      "text": "But actually bandaid is a company."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.61,
      "end": 587.23,
      "text": "So bandages 조금 더..."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.91,
      "end": 588.23,
      "text": "꾸준적인."
    },
    {
      "start": 588.95,
      "end": 589.35,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.91,
      "end": 591.37,
      "text": "But we always say bandaid."
    },
    {
      "start": 591.47,
      "end": 591.79,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 592.09,
      "end": 593.05,
      "text": "It's like 표준아."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.17,
      "end": 593.39,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.39,
      "end": 596.36,
      "text": "And it's..."
    },
    {
      "start": 596.36,
      "end": 597.24,
      "text": "Oh, this is the other."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.38,
      "end": 597.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.72,
      "end": 598.14,
      "text": "Max."
    },
    {
      "start": 598.82,
      "end": 602.0,
      "text": "And it's not that much fun being scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 602.4,
      "end": 605.78,
      "text": "오, 아들의 목소리가 갑자기 탁 들렸을 때 너무 귀여웠는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 606.32,
      "end": 608.84,
      "text": "And it's not that much fun being scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.08,
      "end": 609.8,
      "text": "이렇게 들렸잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 610.34,
      "end": 611.56,
      "text": "It's not that much fun."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.76,
      "end": 614.52,
      "text": "여기까지 끊어서 해석하시면 훨씬 편합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.12,
      "end": 616.36,
      "text": "그렇게 재미없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.28,
      "end": 620.36,
      "text": "Being scary 하는 개라는 거거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.36,
      "end": 624.96,
      "text": "무서워지는 거, 사람들에게 겁주는 거 그다지 재미없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 625.24,
      "end": 626.84,
      "text": "이렇게 해석하시면 자연스러울 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 626.92,
      "end": 628.18,
      "text": "Remember he was bullied?"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.38,
      "end": 628.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 628.88,
      "end": 633.5,
      "text": "And he went to the big bully who bullied him and scared him away."
    },
    {
      "start": 633.6,
      "end": 634.08,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 634.3,
      "end": 637.94,
      "text": "He felt happy for a moment, but then 좀 집집해졌어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.0,
      "end": 638.46,
      "text": "오, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.94,
      "end": 644.02,
      "text": "이 맥스가요, 원래는 친구들한테 짓궂게 놀림을 당하고 그랬었다가"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.02,
      "end": 646.78,
      "text": "갑자기 after being a monster, 그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.98,
      "end": 652.3,
      "text": "몬스터가 되고 나서 놀렸던 친구한테 보복을 하는 그런 장면도 살짝 보였었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.3,
      "end": 655.08,
      "text": "이게 별로 재미없다라는 것도 깨달은 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 655.16,
      "end": 656.74,
      "text": "I like being scary sometimes."
    },
    {
      "start": 656.88,
      "end": 657.52,
      "text": "Sometimes."
    },
    {
      "start": 657.7,
      "end": 658.64,
      "text": "For my kids."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.02,
      "end": 662.26,
      "text": "It's actually kind of lonely."
    },
    {
      "start": 662.78,
      "end": 664.94,
      "text": "It's actually kind of lonely."
    },
    {
      "start": 664.94,
      "end": 670.4,
      "text": "사실 좀 외로워요, 외롭기만 해져요라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 671.16,
      "end": 674.58,
      "text": "I'm sorry, I said all those awful things."
    },
    {
      "start": 674.66,
      "end": 678.5,
      "text": "이번에는 엄마, 엄마가 이야기해주고 있는 부분이었는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 678.84,
      "end": 684.02,
      "text": "I'm sorry, 미안해, I said all those awful things라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 684.02,
      "end": 687.7,
      "text": "내가 그런 심한 말에서 미안해라고 이야기합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 687.7,
      "end": 692.82,
      "text": "Yeah, when we get angry, we say lots of things that we don't mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.82,
      "end": 696.84,
      "text": "that we should not say, even if we do mean them, partially."
    },
    {
      "start": 697.08,
      "end": 698.16,
      "text": "양심이 좀 찔리네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.36,
      "end": 698.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 699.66,
      "end": 702.12,
      "text": "I wouldn't want any other family."
    },
    {
      "start": 702.32,
      "end": 704.9,
      "text": "그러면서도 아주 중요한 메시지를 또 이야기해줍니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 705.02,
      "end": 706.9,
      "text": "I wouldn't want any other family."
    },
    {
      "start": 707.38,
      "end": 710.12,
      "text": "나는 어떤 다른 가족도 원하지 않아."
    },
    {
      "start": 710.12,
      "end": 713.24,
      "text": "우리 가족이 제일 소중해 하는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 713.32,
      "end": 714.14,
      "text": "Bye bye, Dracula."
    },
    {
      "start": 715.2,
      "end": 715.92,
      "text": "가정한테 가라."
    },
    {
      "start": 716.02,
      "end": 716.34,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 716.34,
      "end": 720.72,
      "text": "오, 왠지 이 가족들이 행복한 그런 기분인 것 같은데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 720.88,
      "end": 724.36,
      "text": "At last, the beautiful harmony among them has finally come true."
    },
    {
      "start": 724.52,
      "end": 727.32,
      "text": "It's a happy family, lovey-dovey ending."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.48,
      "end": 730.74,
      "text": "아, 너무 sound sweet한 그런 엔딩인 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 731.02,
      "end": 732.02,
      "text": "Cheezy, but sweet."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.16,
      "end": 732.42,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 733.1,
      "end": 734.94,
      "text": "마지막으로 이 내용 한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 735.97,
      "end": 737.01,
      "text": "You were right, Faye."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.63,
      "end": 739.53,
      "text": "I'm really good at messing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.53,
      "end": 740.37,
      "text": "No, mom."
    },
    {
      "start": 740.79,
      "end": 741.83,
      "text": "You were right."
    },
    {
      "start": 742.55,
      "end": 743.07,
      "text": "I was?"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.21,
      "end": 746.87,
      "text": "It doesn't matter if people look at me and see an ugly mom."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.89,
      "end": 750.11,
      "text": "I know who I am under all these bandages."
    },
    {
      "start": 750.69,
      "end": 753.07,
      "text": "And it's not that much fun being scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 753.43,
      "end": 754.77,
      "text": "It's actually kind of lonely."
    },
    {
      "start": 755.45,
      "end": 758.33,
      "text": "I'm sorry I said all those awful things."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.09,
      "end": 760.89,
      "text": "I wouldn't want any other family."
    },
    {
      "start": 761.87,
      "end": 764.93,
      "text": "That was the most touching moment of this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 765.63,
      "end": 766.15,
      "text": "저는 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.29,
      "end": 766.81,
      "text": "Did you cry?"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.09,
      "end": 769.35,
      "text": "A little bit."
    },
    {
      "start": 769.73,
      "end": 770.37,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.37,
      "end": 771.97,
      "text": "절대 많이는 아니었고."
    },
    {
      "start": 772.09,
      "end": 772.67,
      "text": "Be honest."
    },
    {
      "start": 772.99,
      "end": 773.41,
      "text": "살짝."
    },
    {
      "start": 773.71,
      "end": 774.55,
      "text": "Be honest."
    },
    {
      "start": 775.53,
      "end": 776.71,
      "text": "그런그렁 정도."
    },
    {
      "start": 777.47,
      "end": 778.99,
      "text": "저는 dry eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 779.11,
      "end": 779.49,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 779.81,
      "end": 780.25,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 780.75,
      "end": 781.71,
      "text": "It's an animation."
    },
    {
      "start": 782.17,
      "end": 782.25,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 782.51,
      "end": 782.99,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 783.59,
      "end": 787.59,
      "text": "어쨌든 이 애니메이션으로 우리가 얻을 수 있는 기운도 참 따뜻했습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.81,
      "end": 788.11,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 788.75,
      "end": 791.07,
      "text": "이제 내일부터 9월이에요, 벌써."
    },
    {
      "start": 791.31,
      "end": 791.83,
      "text": "September."
    },
    {
      "start": 791.83,
      "end": 794.95,
      "text": "와, 그럼 우리가 또 새 영화를 만나게 될 텐데."
    },
    {
      "start": 795.35,
      "end": 796.95,
      "text": "Please let us know the name of the movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 797.15,
      "end": 798.91,
      "text": "It's a very, very short name."
    },
    {
      "start": 798.93,
      "end": 799.13,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 799.55,
      "end": 800.69,
      "text": "Just a single word."
    },
    {
      "start": 801.29,
      "end": 801.63,
      "text": "Abe."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.11,
      "end": 802.55,
      "text": "Abe."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.67,
      "end": 803.41,
      "text": "A-B-E."
    },
    {
      "start": 803.57,
      "end": 804.75,
      "text": "아, 이게 답니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 804.97,
      "end": 806.65,
      "text": "It's the name of a character."
    },
    {
      "start": 806.83,
      "end": 808.49,
      "text": "The main character, I think."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.67,
      "end": 808.97,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.97,
      "end": 813.03,
      "text": "그러니까 주연 배우하고 뭔가 관련이 있는 그런 제목인 것 같은데요."
    },
